Summary
-------
This dataset is a modified version of the Beeradvocate dataset of beer ratings (https://data.world/socialmediadata/beeradvocate). It contains average ratings of a subset of beers of the original dataset that were rated by at least 5 consumers.

Attributes
----------
Each beer is rated on five criteria (in this order in the file):
 - appearance,
 - aroma,
 - palate,
 - taste,
 - overall.
Ratings are measured on a scale of 1 to 5.
